titles.title: To suspend temporarily the duty on 1,3,5-Triazine, 2,4,6-tris(2-propenyloxyl)-.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

bill.summary:
2/6/2008--Introduced.
Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on 1,3,5-Triazine, 2,4,6-tris(2-propenyloxyl)-.
